{"tid":2252521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生日自己訂位","createTime":"2020-10-21T13:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T15:03:17.000Z","uid":311329,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfd1eb3b2b7fd5601ac8373d99d9a7d5d708848","tid":2252521,"uid":311329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"好奇問下 <br />\n自己生日訂位同男朋友食飯會唔會好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔關佢唔肯訂事<br />\n純粹咁岩有間野想食<br />\n然後自己book埋因為驚冇位<br />\n<br />\n定係呢啲野應該等佢做<br />\n但又驚佢book唔切喎<br />\n所以想自己黎<br />\n純粹諗緊壽星自己book會唔會好白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca42ec269ed0493fa37e33c5bf4eb7f40cd090","tid":2252521,"uid":29138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"真係好想食就自己book啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係就明示比佢聽<br />\n廢事佢唔記得/搞錯/誤會咗到時嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e826cd956f6cdae4195d7ecb764bd23d3d1ba23","tid":2252521,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"長食長book啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"9e8ac25ff167b45088b98997775c513ea687644e","tid":2252521,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:41:55.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦, 唔洗分得咁清楚"},{"pid":"2dea2b23692c9c97169109810c705e668b11b0de","tid":2252521,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"你自己都唔介意，有咩問題？"},{"pid":"cc567157955698a694a3ee0552416ea6601fd498","tid":2252521,"uid":310637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"你都係想刁難你條仔姐"},{"pid":"7c7d1c4687fdb749f402d597a3b00c0739790164","tid":2252521,"uid":79278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"咁都要諗黎諗去 仲要開post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\"